addEditButtonMouseClicked

private void addEditButtonMouseClicked(java.awt.event.MouseEvent evt)
If no existing product is chosen a new product will be added to the database. Else it will update the current product. The info that is typed in by the user will be validated, and if something is incorrect the fields will be marked with another color.
